<paragraph id="2418850BFF1483E4FC975A66FBA2FD46" blockId="169.[823,1476,517,829]" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1483E4FC975A66FC03FDE6" box="[851,915,518,541]" italics="true" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">Notes.</emphasis>
– The 
<typeStatus id="FB1C3BA9FF1483E4FC245A65FBD0FDE6" box="[992,1088,517,541]" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">holotype</typeStatus>
is a collection folder of two sheets with identical labels and one in flower and the other in fruit. The first author erroneously annotated the sheet with fruiting plants in 1984 as 
<typeStatus id="FB1C3BA9FF1483E4FC305A05FBC3FD86" box="[1012,1107,613,637]" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">holotype</typeStatus>
and the flowering one as isotype. However, they both represent one gathering that was too large to mount on one sheet.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="6CBDD680FF1483E4FC975AA5FA20FCC6" pageId="169" pageNumber="169" type="description">
<paragraph id="2418850BFF1483E4FC975AA5FA20FCC6" blockId="169.[823,1476,517,829]" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">
The systematic position of this taxon has been controversial, and it is tentatively placed here in 
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1483E4FB5C5A86FB7FFD06" box="[1176,1263,742,765]" italics="true" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1483E4FB5C5A86FB7BFD06" box="[1176,1259,742,765]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Brassica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="169" pageNumber="169" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Brassica</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
though that generic assignment is tenuous at best. A summary of the taxonomic confusion is presented under 
<taxonomicName id="E3A7FE88FF1483E4FBB05B45FAB9FCC6" box="[1140,1321,805,829]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Raphanus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="169" pageNumber="169" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aucheri">
<emphasis id="16D35919FF1483E4FBB05B45FAB9FCC6" box="[1140,1321,805,829]" italics="true" pageId="169" pageNumber="169">Raphanus aucheri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see below).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
